reviewText: Classic Christmas TV from the Golden Age of Television.
It was better than I had inticipated.  I loved all the movies.

If I get into the Real Meaning of Christmas, the I will love this Inspirational DVD set! This special holiday DVD features over 2 hours of delightful animated stories about the True Meaning of Christmas. Stories that are perfect for kids and for the young-at-heart! It will help me and my friends learn that JESUS is the Reason for the Season!!
a good re-telling of the classic christmas stories.  the price is right.  and, it is a christmas dvd.  worth the money.
